comments: Sabonis (IND) establishes in a legal position in Rose's (DET) path and places a resting hand on his front that does not affect his ability to defend.
Sabonis (IND) establishes legal position in Rose's (DET) path and firms up but he is able to move through contact.
Kennard (DET) establishes legal position during the pick and makes some contact with Brogdon (IND) during the pick but contact does not affect his ability to defend.
Drummond (DET) extends his arms into Holiday's (IND) back, forcing him into Kennard (DET) while he is in a shooting motion.
Kennard (DET) engages with Holiday (IND) prior to the pick but quickly separate.
Brown (DET) places an arm to Warren's (IND) front during his drive but contact does not affect his SQBR.
Morris (DET) establish legal position in Brogdon's (DET) path and firms up on his side but he is able to move through contact.
Warren (IND) gathers the ball and takes more then two steps.
Sabonis (IND) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position contesting the drive shot attempt by Rose (DET).
Turner (IND) makes some contact with Morris (DET) during the rebound, but contact does not affect his ability to retrieve the ball.
Sabonis (IND) makes contact with Rose's (DET) arm but contact does not affect his SQBR.
Drummond (DET) establishes legal position in Brogdon's (IND) path and slightly extends his arm against his side but contact is marginal.
Turner (IND) makes contact to Rose's (DET) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his drive shot attempt.
Sabonis (IND) makes some contact with Snell (DET) during the pick but he is able to move through contact.
Sabonis (IND) moves to the side of Rose (DET) and slips the contact during his drive to the basket.
Drummond (DET) makes contact with Sabonis (IND) arm during the rebound but contact does not affect his ability to retrieve the ball.
Snell (DET) is in a legal guarding position and Warren (IND) extends his leg to create the marginal contact.
Warren (IND) makes contact with Brown's (DET) arm that affects his SQBR.
Drummond (IND) establishes legal position in Holiday's (IND) path during the screen and firms up but he is able to move through contact.
Holiday (IND) commits a take foul on Kennard (DET).
Sabonis (IND) briefly grasps Browns' (DET) arm during the screen but contact is marginal.
After communicating with the Replay Center at the 00:02.0 mark, the ruling on the floor of a basket interference on Drummond (DET) is confirmed.
